snippet.title: Kurt Cobain Death Investigation: LIVE Discussion : Premonitions?
snippet.description:
Keep an open mind for this live chat , It apparently has been documented that Kurt experienced nightmares, some of which indicated people were out to harm him and in some family were out to kill him. We listen to his ex Tracy speak about that, and listen to Kurt himself talk about violent dreams in an interview from 93. Perhaps that interview is even more reason to think the gun he purchased was FOR PROTECTION and NOT TO KILL HIMSELF ! 
Sources : " Montage Of heck " 
https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/blog/mysteries-consciousness/201912/can-dreams-predict-death
https://medium.com/spiritual-secrets/do-some-people-have-premonitions-about-their-death-af1000192cc5
https://www.sleepfoundation.org/dreams/precognitive-dreams
Buzz interview from YouTube channel @ Daniel S
